ul.li: Travel Package: Represents a travel package offered by the company.
Destination: Represents a specific location included in a travel package.
Activity: Represents an activity that can be enjoyed at a particular destination.
Passenger: Represents a person who signs up for a travel package and can participate in activities.
Create Travel Package: create a new travel package with a name and passenger capacity.
Add Destinations: add destinations to a travel package.
Add Activities: add activities to each destination.
Add Passengers: add passengers to the travel package.
Sign Up for Activities: Passengers can sign up for activities included in the travel package.
Check Availability: The system checks the availability of activities for passengers.
